                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6437" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0125</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7563 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">责先利后：泰山茶溪谷的“变”与“不变”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Responsibility first and benefit later: the &quot;change&quot; and &quot;not change&quot; of Taishan Chaxigu</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙芳，刘菲菲，李佳，郑彬，赵艳（通讯作者），白福萍，梁美丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东泰山茶溪谷农业发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；泰山茶溪谷；SCSR过程模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">corporate social responsibility; Taishan Chaxigu; SCSR process model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泰山茶溪谷沐浴着政策春风，紧跟时代步伐，本着“做好一杯泰山茶”的初心，坚定走有机农业之路，不仅立足泰山环境培育本地特有茶树，更是在脱贫攻坚和乡村振兴战略的大背景下，带动当地农民就业，改变农民观念创富，联结更多利益联合体奔向共同富裕。本案例以泰山茶溪谷为描述主体，展现了企业成立与发展过程中的“利他”价值观，体现了企业社会责任不断升级，但唯心不变的历程，引导学员深入思考企业生存、发展与履行社会责任的决策困境，理解金字塔模型，掌握战略性社会责任过程模型，学会基于具体情境将企业社会责任成功融入其组织战略的具体步骤和方法，为履行战略性企业社会责任提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The Taishan tea Valley is bathed in the spring breeze of policy, keeps up with the pace of the times, and firmly takes the road of organic agriculture in line with the original intention of &quot;making a cup of Taishan tea&quot;. It not only cultivates local unique tea trees based on the Taishan environment, but also drives local farmers&#39; employment, changes farmers&#39; concept, creates wealth, and connects more interest consortia to common prosperity under the background of poverty alleviation and Rural Revitalization Strategy. Taking Taishan chaxi Valley as the description subject, this case shows the &quot;altruistic&quot; values in the process of enterprise establishment and development, reflects the continuous upgrading but idealistic process of corporate social responsibility, guides students to deeply think about the decision-making dilemma of enterprise survival, development and fulfillment of social responsibility, understand the pyramid model, and master the process model of strategic social responsibility, Learn the specific steps and methods to successfully integrate corporate social responsibility into its organizational strategy based on specific situations, so as to provide reference for the performance of strategic corporate social responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金字塔模型；利益相关者理论；履责与竞争优势；SCSR过程模型；识别模型适用边界</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-08</td>
                            </tr>
